{"tid":201475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港產內容農場檢查app　免費幫你封鎖假新聞","createTime":"2017-04-14T18:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T08:03:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0dbed4083cba5d3019f026a284a8284ebcc8c7","tid":201475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:29:38.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017年4月14日<br />\n內容農場（Content Farm）網站專做標題黨出假新聞，近來被廣泛報道，BuzzHand、大榴槤等典型農場亦早已臭名遠播，不過身邊總會有人繼續share。為免誤入農場，許孝謙（Himphen）和他的社會創新團隊Collaction開發出一個app「內容農場檢查器」。一入農場網站就會彈出警告。如果阿爸阿媽搞不清真假新聞經常share農場，不妨幫長輩們裝上此app。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ygZdKXzAO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_ygZdKXzAO8&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=3179f56c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ygZdKXzAO8</a>"},{"pid":"90d4a0b57056fe37402b13fa6cf3b59127d129e4","tid":201475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d3a952cc394f4741b6d013972c24ba31ef169f","tid":201475,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T19:07:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以出IOS version？<br />\n我老母以至親戚都用iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf41db13cbb0cefd3d6e28bc35c585d8b2e9822","tid":201475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T20:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b016315b13a9062d2139e772f0ec9fa034b516a","tid":201475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T22:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d98fbd5d322c205cfe558c42619d911d54d6eb","tid":201475,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T23:45:55.000Z","msg